        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Yes, but mobs will only begin to summon when a certain amount of damage has been done to them.  I believe this is a percentage of their hp in the 5% range, but it may be a fixed amount, not sure.</P><P>Thats why you can kite around summoning mobs like Gorenaire all day, but as soon as you do enough damage to em you're getting summoned.</P><P>Daedrea Darksoul</font></td>
