        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> You used to be able to /assist Feared NPC's, that way you could control your agro by seeing who the mob was pissed at. So when fear would break, the npc would summon your pet instead of you. I used this to solo elder wyverns etc, without ever getting summoned(after several trys of course). To do this now, basically do the same thing, control your agro. Make it so the mob is more pissed at the pet than you.</P><P>Muerte<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=29253" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=29253</a></font></td>
